50)

 

 

Miss Chance=1/4

 

 

 

 

Bonuses:

Armour (+HP)Better weapons (+Attack) Increased
Intellect (+miss chance, obviously +intellect)





 

Abbreviations:

Att – Attack

Inl – Intellect

HP – Hit points

Op… - Opponent’s..(E.g. Att)

 

First Move – Processes intellect and decides who has the
first turn.

Move – What user decides to do.

Scare – Try to scare the opponent away.

 

 

 

